                </dt>
                <dd class="inline">We value collaboration and teamwork. You'll work alongside talented individuals who share your passion and dedication to excellence.</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="relative pl-9">
                <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-logo-color dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
